# LangGraph Chatbot with MongoDB Memory ğŸ§ ğŸ’¾

This project demonstrates how to build a **LangGraph-based chatbot** that stores **persistent chat history in MongoDB** using `MongoDBSaver`.

Unlike in-memory storage, this setup ensures that conversation history is **not lost when the application restarts**.

---

## âœ¨ Features

- âœ… LangGraph state-based chatbot
- âœ… Persistent chat history using MongoDB
- âœ… Thread-based conversations (`thread_id`)
- âœ… Uses OpenAI chat models
- âœ… Production-ready memory storage

